text: József Komatits (6 November 1950 - 19 June 2007) was a Hungarian fencer. He competed in the individual and team foil events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2007 deaths Category:Hungarian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Hungary Category:Fencers at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Szombathely
